s=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-maras-salt-mines\">Maras Salt Mines<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hidden behind a hill, deep in the Sacred Valley is a landscape of white terraced baths better known as the Maras Salt Mines. This ancient Incan technique of extracting salt, by hand, is still used today, which is impressive to see from close-by.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131140\/peru-local-598x810.jpg\" alt=\"peru local\"><\/noscript><img width=\"249\" height=\"338\" alt=\"peru local\" data-id=\"17048\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=17048\" class=\"wp-image-17048 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131140\/peru-local-598x810.jpg 598w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131140\/peru-local-300x406.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131140\/peru-local-600x813.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131140\/peru-local-249x338.jpg 249w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131140\/peru-local-443x600.jpg 443w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131140\/peru-local-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131140\/peru-local-120x163.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131140\/peru-local-133x180.jpg 133w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131140\/peru-local-567x768.jpg 567w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/