altinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131147\/sacred-valley-peru-Maras-Salt-Mines.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-moray-terraces\">Moray Terraces<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Close to the Maras Salt Mines is Moray. One of the most phenomenal, and somewhat mind-blowing, things to see in Sacred Valley. These circular terraces, also named &#x2018;The Laboratory&#x2019;, offer changing light and temperature conditions at each level. For that reason, they could experiment with many different kinds of crops and which is the reason why Peru, nowadays, has over 2000 species of potatoes!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>See all the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/things-to-do-cusco\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"things to do in Cusco, Peru (opens in a new tab)\">things to do in Cusco, Peru<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131137\/Moray-Terraces-sacred-valley-peru.jpg\" alt=\"Moray Terraces sacred valley peru\"><\/noscript><img wid