ing Machu Picchu including the train ride will take you a full day.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Here&#x2019;s the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/machu-picchu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Complete Machu Picchu Guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131111\/Aguas-Calientes-lady-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"Aguas Calientes lady\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Aguas Calientes lady\" data-id=\"17066\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=17066\" class=\"wp-image-17066 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131111\/Aguas-Calientes-lady-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131111\/Aguas-Calientes-lady-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131111\/Aguas-Calientes-lady-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131111\/Aguas-Calientes-lady-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131111\/Aguas-Calientes-lady-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131111\/Aguas-C