Cusco Ticket<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The ticket options are wide therefore making visiting Sacred Valley a bit confusing. The &#x2018;Boleto Turistico&#x2019; is the main ticket which gives access to almost all of the archaeological sites, museums, and Sacred Valley. This tourist ticket is valid for 10 days starting from the first site you will visit, giving entrance to 16 different sites. The &#x2018;&#x2018;Boleto Turistico&#x2019; Sacred Valley ticket costs 130 SOL (38.5 USD) and gives access to the following three ticket options:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131030\/Ollantaytambo-tour-620x810.jpg\" alt=\"Ollantaytambo tour\"><\/noscript><img width=\"259\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Ollantaytambo tour\" data-id=\"17106\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=17106\" class=\"wp-image-17106 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131030\/Ollantaytambo-tour-620x810.jpg 620w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131030\/Ollantaytambo-tour-300x392.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131030\/Ollantaytambo-tour-600x784.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131030\/Ollantaytambo-tour-259x338.jpg 259w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131030\/Ollantaytambo-tour-459x600.jpg 459w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131030\/Ollantaytambo-tour-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131030\/Ollantaytambo-tour-125x163.jpg 125w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uplo