pg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru.jpg 1484w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131033\/Ollantaytambo-peru-626x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>First ticket:&#xA0; <\/strong>Sacsayhuaman, Qenqo, Pukapukara, and Tambomachay.&#xA0;<br><br><strong>Second ticket: <\/strong>Museo de Arte Popular, Museo de Sitio del Qoricancha, Museo Historico Regional, Museo de Arte Contemporaneo, Monumento a Pachacuteq Centro Qosqo de Arte Nativo, Pikillacta, and Tipon.<br><br><strong>Third ticket<\/strong>: Pisac, Ollantaytambo, Chinchero, and Moray.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You cannot buy separate tickets for these individual sites but if you&#x2019;re on a budget you can buy a ticket for only one part of the valley. We would say ticket 3 is the more impressive but if you&#x2019;re more into museums ticket 2 might be better for you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131051\/train-peru.jpg\" alt=\"train peru\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"304\" alt=\"train peru\" class=\"wp-image-17100 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131051\/train-peru.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131051\/train-peru-300x203.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131051\/train-peru-600x405.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131051\/train-peru-450x304.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131051\/train-peru-800x540.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131051\/train-peru-1080x730.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131051\/train-peru-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131051\/train-peru-163x110.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\