et=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Machu Picchu and the Machu Picchu tickets (opens in a new tab)\">Machu Picchu and the Machu Picchu tickets<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru.jpg\" alt=\"Rainbow Mountain peru\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"317\" alt=\"Rainbow Mountain peru\" class=\"wp-image-17104 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru-600x423.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru-450x317.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru-800x564.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru-1080x762.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru-163x115.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru-255x180.jpg 255w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru-768x542.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23131037\/Rainbow-Mountain-peru-1024x722.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10